PHPTAL Module for ZendFramework2

This Module is a draft for a PHPTAL integration in ZendFramework.

Features:

- Uses Zend\View\Resolver to resolve template files. 
    This allows to keep the template file location 
    configuration from the Zend\View\Renderer\PhpRenderer



The Source is tried to be as close as possible to the ZTal solution
(https://github.com/namesco/ZTal)